{"tid":1054304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"理大集會賣小強 學生關sir何俊謙稱患情緒病：與家人決裂 無家可歸","createTime":"2019-03-09T17:25:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T10:29:39.000Z","uid":2748,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"30a472753eb905037da8ab3ca529ec16782a30fc","tid":1054304,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T17:25:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/K6QeWkq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FK6QeWkq.png&h=2dde2627&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n學渣禁錮侮辱師長，理大大義滅親嚴正懲處。可恨的是，理大學生會昨晚在校內舉行集會，聲援被處分的4名學渣，出席者包括不同院校的學生代表，更有一堆黃政棍如「毛婆」毛孟靜、「快必」譚得志、黃浩銘，現場更見「香港獨立」旗幟。最Kai男主角、被踢出校的港獨何俊謙<span style=\"color: red;\">大賣小強，聲稱與家人決裂，無家可歸，仲話自己開始有情緒病添。</span><br />\n<br />\n反問師長是否尊重學生<br />\n<br />\n集會前，理大學生會內務副會長胡國泓向校方代表遞交請願信，強迫理大撤回對同學的處罰。何俊謙除咗賣苦話自己連屋企都冇埋之外，自然要繼續發噏瘋，指責理大高層是中共的爪牙，又帶領在場人士辱罵理大校董劉炳章。何又話校方處罰犯事的四件學渣，理大學生會因此承受巨大輿論壓力云云。<br />\n<br />\n而被罰停課一年的學生會前會長林穎恒指自己唔後悔，更叫人繼續「抗爭」。林同時無賴指尊重是否單向，反問「師長是否需要尊重學生」喎？尊重的確係雙向嘅，但犯事學生對師長零尊重，更用粗鄙言行侮辱師長，既然如此，林穎恒憑乜講尊重？<br />\n<br />\n理大再發聲明拒忍暴力<br />\n<br />\n理大昨晚再發聲明，指犯事學生當日「行為粗暴，態度囂張」，校方必須嚴肅處理，並強調與言論自由無關。理大重申，校方非常重視學生行為操守，不會容忍任何粗暴行為在校園內出現。<br />\n<br />\n原圖：無綫新聞截圖、香港大學學生會學苑即時新聞 Undergrad, H.K.U.S.U. Instant News Facebook<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/undergradnews/photos/pb.393883453958717.-2207520000.1552009009./3118274148186287/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fundergradnews%2Fphotos%2Fpb.393883453958717.-2207520000.1552009009.%2F3118274148186287%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2JugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=b0fa09ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/undergradnews/photos/pb.393883453958717.-2207520000.1552009009./3118274148186287/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"a027b95f3909a4ab6aefd6ed0e9ff1f3bae94d28","tid":1054304,"uid":2748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T17:43:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a756941cf80bba2ea388dc7c17b86efaa2eb5470","tid":1054304,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T18:16:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71600b94be26cfcb41f3404dade97bdba1deddcf","tid":1054304,"uid":48234,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T02:28:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">請問CardPay(會員#2748)你屙尿嗰陣起左腳定右腳?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1042857\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1042857</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"155e134b2a6f5b9e90d35f592d812e5c20d07334","tid":1054304,"uid":42820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T02:29:46.000Z","msg":"還有党"},{"pid":"4dee3c255dd89e9bb028be71368aa92fb6a26cb3","tid":1054304,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T05:13:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805526a883000c0df713cccb5818cb96c1f983b2","tid":1054304,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:13:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f87f1ca94d50d01f883c4fb09b463b44756f5b41","tid":1054304,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:25:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b7d3